Subject: [PATCH] SwiftDriver: use CMake's Swift compilation mode abstraction

CMake 3.29 introduced CMP0157 and split Swift compilation from linking when
using the Ninja generator. SwiftDriver still selects the old policy through its
3.19 minimum, so CMake 4.x emits a combined incremental compile-and-link
command for every executable.

When Ninja needs to relink one of those executables without recompiling its
unchanged Swift source, the Swift driver fails while resolving its synthesized
module output:

    error: cannotResolveTempPath(main-1.swiftmodule)

Select the modern policy when the installed CMake supports it. This retains
incremental compilation while giving Ninja distinct object compilation and
link actions. Give hyphenated executable targets valid Swift module names for
the split compilation graph. Older supported CMake releases keep the existing
behavior.

Sentinel: NUCLEUS_SWIFT_DRIVER_CMAKE_SWIFT_COMPILATION_MODE

diff --git a/CMakeLists.txt b/CMakeLists.txt
index 21e0f99c..77edc25f 100644
--- a/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -15,6 +15,10 @@ if(POLICY CMP0091)
   cmake_policy(SET CMP0091 NEW)
 endif()
 
+if(POLICY CMP0157)
+  cmake_policy(SET CMP0157 NEW)
+endif()
+
 project(SwiftDriver
   LANGUAGES C CXX Swift)

diff --git a/Sources/swift-build-sdk-interfaces/CMakeLists.txt b/Sources/swift-build-sdk-interfaces/CMakeLists.txt
index fa1cd9c1..26bd4ad7 100644
--- a/Sources/swift-build-sdk-interfaces/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/Sources/swift-build-sdk-interfaces/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -8,6 +8,8 @@
 
 add_executable(swift-build-sdk-interfaces
   main.swift)
+set_target_properties(swift-build-sdk-interfaces PROPERTIES
+  Swift_MODULE_NAME swift_build_sdk_interfaces)
 target_link_libraries(swift-build-sdk-interfaces PUBLIC
   SwiftDriver
   SwiftDriverExecution)
diff --git a/Sources/swift-driver/CMakeLists.txt b/Sources/swift-driver/CMakeLists.txt
index f4ecac18..14358d60 100644
--- a/Sources/swift-driver/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/Sources/swift-driver/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -8,6 +8,8 @@
 
 add_executable(swift-driver
   main.swift)
+set_target_properties(swift-driver PROPERTIES
+  Swift_MODULE_NAME swift_driver)
 target_link_libraries(swift-driver PUBLIC
   SwiftDriver
   SwiftDriverExecution)
diff --git a/Sources/swift-help/CMakeLists.txt b/Sources/swift-help/CMakeLists.txt
index 9c52178d..14bc3221 100644
--- a/Sources/swift-help/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/Sources/swift-help/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -8,7 +8,9 @@
 
 add_executable(swift-help
   main.swift)
+set_target_properties(swift-help PROPERTIES
+  Swift_MODULE_NAME swift_help)
 target_link_libraries(swift-help PUBLIC
   SwiftOptions
   ArgumentParser
   TSCBasic)
